      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Gaurdrails:\n\nIn Dev, Your LLM will behave well . Testing will happend around the cases based on the\napplication feature, usecase and acceptance Criteria\n\nIn production, you face some unpredictable users, different kind of input, hackers may i\ntry to leak the data .\n\nIn order to gaurd your application without getting harmed or collapse, your gaurdrails\nremains first and last line of defense.\n \n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Gaurdrails:\n\nIn Dev, Your LLM will behave well . Testing will happend around the cases based on the application feature, usecase and acceptance Criteria\n\nIn production, you face some unpredictable users, different kind of input, hackers may i try to leak the data .\n\nIn order to gaurd your application without getting harmed or collapse, your gaurdrails remains first and last line of defense.\n \n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
