      "updated": 1780237636593,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Gaurdrails Architecture:\n\n-> Input Filter -> PII Redaction with help of regex patterns\n-> Semantic Filter -> Embedding to detect unsafe topic\n-> Policy prompt -> Refusal rules.\n-> Output filter -> After output generation\n-> Agent Gaurdrail -> tool calls, scope validation\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Gaurdrails Architecture:\n\n-> Input Filter -> PII Redaction with help of regex patterns\n-> Semantic Filter -> Embedding to detect unsafe topic\n-> Policy prompt -> Refusal rules.\n-> Output filter -> After output generation\n-> Agent Gaurdrail -> tool calls, scope validation\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
