      "text": "PII detection:\n\n-> Direct PII - Email,address, phone number, SSN, Aadhar.\n -> Indirect PII - Location details, employer Details, Medical details\n-> Contextutal PII - comes from Documents ( RAG)\n-> Reverse PII - if model provides some kind of random PII information during the output\n\n\n",
